dct_title_s: Hydrographic map of Delavan and Lauderdale lakes. Walworth Co., Wisconsin
dct_description_sm: Contour interval = 10 ft.; At head of cover title: no. 6.; Explanation of map on 2nd page of cover.; Shows roads, parks, hotels, drainage, etc.; Depth shown by hypsometric tints, bathymetric isolines and soundings.; Includes 9 cross sections.
